%% 图2-2 LLM Agent ReAct框架工作机制图
%% Figure 2-2 LLM Agent ReAct Framework Working Mechanism Diagram

flowchart TD
    Start(["用户任务输入"])
    Profile["档案模块 Profile<br/>角色定义 + 能力边界"]
    Memory["记忆模块 Memory<br/>短期工作记忆 + 长期持久记忆"]
    LLM{"LLM 推理引擎<br/>(GPT-4o / Claude / GLM)"}

    subgraph ReAct["ReAct 循环"]
        direction TB
        Thought["思考 Thought<br/>(Chain-of-Thought 显式推理)"]
        Action["行动 Action<br/>(选择并执行工具)"]
        Obs["观察 Observation<br/>(接收工具返回结果)"]

        Thought --> Action --> Obs --> Thought
    end

    Tools["工具注册表 Tool Registry<br/>查询档案 / 检索 JD / 调用 API"]
    Done{"任务完成?"}
    Final(["最终答案<br/>Final Answer"])

    Start --> Profile --> LLM
    Memory <--> LLM
    LLM --> Thought
    Action <--> Tools
    Obs --> Done
    Done -->|否| Thought
    Done -->|是| Final

    classDef startend fill:#e8eaf6,stroke:#3949ab,stroke-width:2px
    classDef module fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#f57c00,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef llm fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c2185b,stroke-width:2px
    classDef cycle fill:#f1f8e9,stroke:#558b2f,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef tool fill:#e0f7fa,stroke:#00838f,stroke-width:1.5px

    class Start,Final startend
    class Profile,Memory module
    class LLM llm
    class Thought,Action,Obs cycle
    class Tools,Done tool
